column16: Didi Gregorius singles on a ground ball to left fielder Corey Dickerson.   Brett Gardner scores.  Gary Sanchez out at home on the throw, left fielder Corey Dickerson to catcher Wilson Ramos.
Adam Kolarek intentionally walks Gary Sanchez.
Aaron Judge grounds out, third baseman Evan Longoria to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Brett Gardner to 2nd.
Clint Frazier called out on strikes.
Brett Gardner grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Joey Gallo singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mallex Smith.
Carlos Gomez grounds out, pitcher Adam Kolarek to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Rays challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Rougned Odor grounds out, second baseman Brad Miller to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Yonder Alonso hit by pitch.    Marcus Semien to 2nd.
Matt Joyce lines out to center fielder Mallex Smith.
Nick Franklin grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Martin Maldonado grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.
C.  J.   Cron homers (3) on a fly ball to right field.    Andrelton Simmons scores.
Kole Calhoun hit by pitch.    Cameron Maybin to 2nd.
Jackie Bradley grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Hanley Ramirez homers (13) on a fly ball to right field.
Mitch Moreland flies out to left fielder Corey Dickerson.
Javier Baez flies out to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.
Albert Almora lines out to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.
Ian Happ singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mallex Smith.   Kris Bryant scores.    Anthony Rizzo scores.
Ben Zobrist out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Adam Kolarek to first baseman Logan Morrison.   Kris Bryant to 3rd.    Anthony Rizzo to 2nd.
Anthony Rizzo singles on a line drive to left fielder Corey Dickerson.   Kris Bryant to 2nd.
Joey Rickard grounds into a double play, second baseman Taylor Featherston to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.   Craig Gentry out at 2nd.
Ruben Tejada flies out to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.
Craig Gentry reaches on a force attempt, missed catch error by second baseman Taylor Featherston, assist to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.    Welington Castillo to 2nd.
Chris Stewart grounds into a force out, fielded by shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.   Gregory Polanco out at 2nd.
Gregory Polanco grounds into a force out, second baseman Tim Beckham to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.   John Jaso out at 2nd.    Gregory Polanco to 1st.
John Jaso singles on a ground ball to center fielder Steven Souza Jr.
With John Jaso batting, Andrew McCutchen caught stealing 3rd base, catcher Jesus Sucre to third baseman Evan Longoria.
